Roma!

419
00:49:09,229 --> 00:49:10,229
Roma!

420
00:49:54,109 --> 00:49:55,148
Beba isso.

421
00:49:55,909 --> 00:49:57,109
Vai se sentir melhor.

422
00:50:01,949 --> 00:50:03,428
<i>Talvez,</i>

423
00:50:03,869 --> 00:50:05,749
<i>tudo isso seja por causa do pente.</i>

424
00:50:06,548 --> 00:50:07,909
L e G.

425
00:50:08,629 --> 00:50:10,469
Lisa Grigorieva.

426
00:50:12,548 --> 00:50:13,628
Lisa.

427
00:50:15,229 --> 00:50:16,549
Suicida.

428
00:50:17,909 --> 00:50:20,029
Como sabe que ela cometeu suicídio?

429
00:50:21,389 --> 00:50:24,389
